item.title: Web Dev
item.description: Connectivity is a phenomenal power we’ve got. Today, the whole world is connected by some or the other means. Technologically these mediums are desktops, mobile phones, tablets, smart wearable devices and the list goes on. But how does this all happen, how does data gets from one point to another? How does different devices and applications connect with each other and how does they allow us to shop, book a flight and order food?
